<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verse</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

    <div
      class="row g-3 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3"
      style="margin-left: 60px; margin-right: 60px"
    >
      <div class="feature col">
        <div
          class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-2 mb-3"
        >
          <img
            src="/henry-be-TCsCykbwSJw-unsplash.jpg"
            style="height: 300px; width: 420px"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Literary Sanctuary</h3>
        <p>
          What secrets do books hold? Join us as we uncover the<br />
          hidden meanings and messages within the pages.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="icon-link">
          Read More →
          <svg class="bi"><use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature col">
        <div
          class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-2 mb-3"
          style="border-radius:5px inset:100px "
        >
          <img
            src="/nasa-hubble-space-telescope-Ihr52Kmvg5Y-unsplash.jpg"
            style="height: 300px; width: 420px"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Voyager's Journey</h3>
        <p>
          The Voyager probes have been exploring the outer reaches<br />
          of our solar system for over 40 years.Learn about the history<br />
          of the Voyager missions, their scientific discoveries, and the ongoing
          journey.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="icon-link">
          Read More→
          <svg class="bi"><use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature col">
        <div
          class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-2 mb-3"
        >
          <img
            src="/nasa-8Hjx3GNZYeA-unsplash.jpg"
            style="height: 300px; width: 420px"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Celestial View</h3>
        <p>
          NASA has recently released a breathtaking image of Earth captured from
          space. The image, taken by a satellite orbiting our planet, showcases
          the intricate beauty of our world.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="icon-link">
          Read More→
          <svg class="bi"><use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container my-5">
      <div
        class="position-relative p-5 text-center text-muted bg-body border border-dashed rounded-5"
      >
        <svg class="bi mt-5 mb-3" width="48" height="48">
          <use xlink:href="#check2-circle"></use>
        </svg>
        <h1 class="text-body-emphasis">Create Your Own Post</h1>
        <p class="col-lg-6 mx-auto mb-4">
          Start sharing your insights and ideas with the world. Click below to
          create a new post effortlessly.
        </p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary px-5 mb-5" href="/create&view" role="button">
          Get Started
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
